snippet.title: Kellie and Kimbra in the Moment
snippet.description: Kellie Nicholson and Kimbra Westervelt invite guests to share their stories about the journey to success, the heartbreak of failure and how creativity fuels their personal growth.  The ladies also discuss hot topics, thought-provoking issues and moral dilemmas.  Their mission is to inspire others, encourage debate and help others embrace new paradigms as we move forward in an ever-changing world.
